1
00:01:15,239 --> 00:01:16,680
We've found the Water Cloud Rhinoceros.

2
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:19,640
But what's still on your mind?

3
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:24,719
I thought destroying it

4
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:27,560
would stop Red Heart from being reborn.

5
00:01:29,159 --> 00:01:30,719
But no matter what I do,

6
00:01:31,319 --> 00:01:32,640
it won't be damaged.

7
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,560
I can try

8
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:44,799
to help you destroy it.

9
00:01:50,359 --> 00:01:52,040
The last two lines of You Wencai's poem

10
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:54,120
should be the way to destroy the Water Cloud Rhinoceros.

11
00:01:55,239 --> 00:01:56,319
Shattered Dreams with Lingering Affection,

12
00:01:56,319 --> 00:01:57,280
Heaven and Earth Overturned,

13
00:01:58,200 --> 00:02:00,120
Profound Amber sinks into the Abyss,

14
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:02,239
Calamity's End.

15
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,239
I can't figure it out.

16
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,799
Are you forgiving me

17
00:02:09,079 --> 00:02:10,240
by telling me

18
00:02:12,479 --> 00:02:13,360
the last line?

19
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:16,000
You truly repented in the Pavilion.

20
00:02:17,319 --> 00:02:19,159
Little Bell Spirit has forgiven you.

21
00:02:24,319 --> 00:02:26,159
Do you mean something else

22
00:02:26,879 --> 00:02:28,080
by the last line?

23
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:30,039
It's a pity to lose the Amber,

24
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,120
but all the disasters

25
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,560
all the misfortune and calamity

26
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:34,039
will come to an end,

27
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:35,840
and a bright future will come.

28
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,599
You've sacrificed so much for the Demon Clan.

29
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,599
You will surely get what you want.

30
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:45,319
I'll take your blessing.

31
00:02:52,599 --> 00:02:53,240
Look.

32
00:02:53,479 --> 00:02:54,199
So beautiful.

33
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:57,759
No wonder the pig demon named this new barrier

34
00:02:58,039 --> 00:02:59,240
"Stars Falling in the Milky Way".

35
00:02:59,759 --> 00:03:00,199
Alas.

36
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:00,879
Look.

37
00:03:14,199 --> 00:03:15,120
A pretty name.

38
00:03:17,319 --> 00:03:18,520
But as the stars fall

39
00:03:19,439 --> 00:03:20,319
into the darkness,

40
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,599
the beauty

41
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,240
is just an illusion.

42
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:27,280
Stars do fall,

43
00:03:28,319 --> 00:03:29,759
but there's always a glimmer in the dark.

44
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,400
Good things

45
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,879
come and go.

46
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,719
I thought

47
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,240
becoming a demon queen

48
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,840
meant I was damned forever.

49
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,199
But I found

50
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:45,120
the one I should treat with all my heart.

51
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:52,680
Good things keep coming.

52
00:03:54,479 --> 00:03:55,360
Don't worry.

53
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:27,199
Shen Que.

54
00:04:27,199 --> 00:04:27,639
Ah?

55
00:04:30,879 --> 00:04:31,959
You're not him.

56
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,959
♪Past dreams are as distant as the sky.♪

57
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:04,079
♪If we were not meant to be in the past life,♪

58
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,600
would you give me a chance now?

59
00:05:18,399 --> 00:05:19,920
We were different species.

60
00:05:21,079 --> 00:05:22,319
Now we're both demons,

61
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:24,839
yet we're more distant than ever.

62
00:05:27,639 --> 00:05:28,759
Distance isn't just

63
00:05:29,519 --> 00:05:31,120
between humans and demons.

64
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:33,480
Love, hate, karma...

65
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,040
Life is unpredictable.

66
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:24,600
A'Li,

67
00:06:25,079 --> 00:06:26,480
I'll ask master tomorrow

68
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,240
to bless our marriage.

69
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,040
Good.

70
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,839
Do wishes made at Xianyin Pool

71
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,399
really come true?

72
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:37,240
Legend has it

73
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:39,759
the other end of the pool is the River of Forgotten Dust,

74
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,120
the Water of Destiny,

75
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:43,360
which can help people fulfill their wishes.

76
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:46,360
Water of Destiny?

77
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,360
Yes.

78
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:50,560
It is said that only demons that appear once in a hundred years

79
00:06:50,759 --> 00:06:52,160
can find the spring.

80
00:06:52,639 --> 00:06:55,079
Even the hardest things

81
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,600
will be destroyed instantly

82
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,879
in the spring.

83
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,600
Give me one.

84
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:04,759
Shattered dreams, overturned heaven and earth.

85
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:07,920
Amber sinks, abyss claims, end of fate.

86
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,759
Shattered dreams,

87
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:12,879
overturned world,

88
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:15,120
Amber sinks, abyss claims, end of fate.

89
00:07:22,279 --> 00:07:23,360
So it is.

90
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,160
The world

91
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,759
is indeed a cycle of cause and effect,

92
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:31,120
beyond words.

93
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,480
A'Li,

94
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,560
where are you going?

95
00:07:40,319 --> 00:07:42,360
I know how to destroy the Water Cloud Rhinoceros.

96
00:07:43,079 --> 00:07:44,279
Shattered dreams,

97
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,319
That's me.

98
00:07:46,279 --> 00:07:48,079
Only I can destroy the Water Cloud Rhinoceros.

99
00:07:48,319 --> 00:07:50,040
It's not just your fight.

100
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,360
It's the safety of the entire clan.

101
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,959
I've always left you alone.

102
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,160
This time,

103
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,639
we'll face it together.

104
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:58,720
And me.

105
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,439
It's time.

106
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:22,879
Go.

107
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:25,879
Take back what's ours.

108
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:32,240
Xu Qinglai must've sensed the rhino's return.

109
00:08:32,439 --> 00:08:34,559
He's been targeting the demon's lair,

110
00:08:34,879 --> 00:08:36,000
but in reality,

111
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,840
he's after the Water Cloud Rhinoceros.

112
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:40,120
We must split into two groups,

113
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,679
one to the Xianyin Pool,

114
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:43,320
to destroy the rhinoceros

115
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,080
while the other holds Xu Qinglai

116
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,919
and defends the lair.

117
00:08:47,159 --> 00:08:49,080
I can mobilize the guards

118
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,639
to hold Xu Qinglai.

119
00:08:56,759 --> 00:08:57,399
Don't worry,

120
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,559
my men are loyal

121
00:08:59,759 --> 00:09:00,639
They're loyal and reliable.

122
00:09:01,159 --> 00:09:03,120
I'll also take the chance to go to Qingdu Temple

123
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:05,519
to find out about Chi Xin and Xu Qinglai.

124
00:09:06,039 --> 00:09:07,360
So we can be prepared.

125
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:11,120
Okay.

126
00:09:11,679 --> 00:09:12,919
Let Bai follow you.

127
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,200
You can help each other.

128
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:16,639
Okay.

129
00:09:22,159 --> 00:09:22,720
Qinglan.

130
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:24,960
There's something only you can help me with.

131
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:26,200
Please tell me.

132
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:27,840
I'll be brief.

133
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,559
the State Preceptor, Xu Qinglai,

134
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:31,759
has been secretly raising the fragments of Chi Xin's soul.

135
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,559
Once the soul is restored,

136
00:09:33,879 --> 00:09:35,279
the mortal realm will become a living hell.

137
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:38,320
His scheme is just one step away from success.

138
00:09:38,559 --> 00:09:40,759
I need you to stall the demon hunters

139
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,240
of Qingdu Temple to buy me time.

140
00:09:42,519 --> 00:09:43,320
Your Highness, rest assured.

141
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:44,399
Leave it to me.

142
00:09:46,519 --> 00:09:47,480
This is perilous.

143
00:09:48,399 --> 00:09:49,759
I need you to think carefully.

144
00:09:50,279 --> 00:09:52,120
I'll give it my all.

145
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:50,519
He's dead.

146
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:51,960
He's dead.

147
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,759
The Red Heart wasn't on him.

148
00:11:02,919 --> 00:11:03,559
No!

149
00:11:03,679 --> 00:11:04,799
A'Li is in danger.

150
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:09,759
Qinglan has fallen.

151
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,159
I'll draw them away.

152
00:11:13,159 --> 00:11:14,039
You go warn A'Li.

153
00:11:14,039 --> 00:11:15,279
The Red Heart isn't in Qingdu Temple.

154
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:17,159
[The Bone Sword is a sacred weapon.]

155
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,039
[Only with blood sacrifice]

156
00:11:18,039 --> 00:11:19,120
[can it slay evil spirits.]

157
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:20,600
Defeating him

158
00:11:20,759 --> 00:11:21,600
requires your help.

159
00:11:23,519 --> 00:11:24,279
What are you doing?

160
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:26,000
This battle is a matter of life and death.

161
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,360
The Demon Clan cannot afford to lose.

162
00:11:28,039 --> 00:11:29,639
I'll transfer some of my power to you.

163
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:43,960
You go first.

164
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:44,759
Be careful!
